---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About navfolio"
  description="A calm personal publication starter for links, notes, writing, and profile content."
  pubDate={new Date('May 01 2026')}
  heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
  <p>
    navfolio is a small personal publication starter built for people who want a clear place to
    collect profile details, useful links, project notes, and long-form writing.
  </p>

  <p>
    The default content is intentionally fictional. Replace the sample profile, links, GitHub
    username, and blog posts with your own information in `src/data/profile.ts` and
    `src/content/blog/`.
  </p>

  <p>
    The publication space is static by default, so it is easy to host on GitHub Pages, Vercel,
    Netlify, Cloudflare Pages, or any platform that can build an Astro project.
  </p>
</Layout>
